{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}
    About Zorglux
{% endblock %}

{% block body_header %}
    {% include '@common/navbar.html.twig' %}
{% endblock %}

{% block body_content %}
    <twig:Container>
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold mb-5">Everyone has a story to tell</h1>
        <section id="about" class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="text-2xl mb-2 font-bold">1. What is Zorglux?</h2>
            <p>Zorglux is a dynamic platform designed for bloggers of all kinds to share their stories, ideas, and
                experiences with a wide audience. Whether you’re a seasoned writer or just starting out, Zorglux offers the
                tools and community to help your voice be heard.</p>
            <br>
            <h3 class="mb-2 font-bold">Our Mission</h3>
            <p>Our mission at Zorglux is to empower individuals to express themselves freely and connect with others through
                meaningful content. We believe in the power of stories to inspire, inform, and unite people from all walks
                of life. By providing an inclusive platform, we aim to foster a vibrant community where diverse voices are
                celebrated.</p>
            <br>

            <h3 class="mb-2 font-bold">Why Choose Zorglux?</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc ml-5">
                <li>Easy-to-use blogging tools that cater to both beginners and experienced bloggers.</li>
                <li>A supportive community that encourages interaction and growth.</li>
                <li>Customizable blog templates to help you create a unique online presence.</li>
                <li>SEO-friendly platform to help your content reach a larger audience.</li>
                <li>Regular updates and new features to enhance your blogging experience.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="features" class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="text-2xl mb-2 font-bold">2. Features of Zorglux</h2>
            <p>Zorglux offers a range of features designed to make blogging simple, enjoyable, and effective:</p>
            <ul class="ml-5 list-disc">
                <li><strong>Customizable Templates:</strong> Choose from a variety of blog templates to match your style.
                    Easily adjust layouts, fonts, and colors to create a blog that represents you.
                </li>
                <li><strong>SEO Tools:</strong> Utilize built-in tools to optimize your content for search engines, helping
                    you attract more readers and grow your audience.
                </li>
                <li><strong>Community Engagement:</strong> Connect with other bloggers and readers through comments, likes,
                    and social sharing. Foster meaningful interactions and build a loyal following.
                </li>
                <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Track your blog’s performance with detailed analytics and insights.
                    Understand your audience better and tailor your content to meet their needs.
                </li>
                <li><strong>Monetization Options:</strong> Explore various monetization options, such as ads and sponsored
                    content, to turn your passion for blogging into a source of income.
                </li>
                <li><strong>Mobile-Friendly:</strong> Zorglux ensures your blog looks great on any device, making it easy
                    for readers to access your content on the go.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="community" class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="text-2xl mb-2 font-bold">3. Join the Zorglux Community</h2>
            <p>At Zorglux, we believe in the power of community. Our platform is designed to help you connect with
                like-minded individuals, share your passions, and grow your network.</p><br>
            <ul class="ml-5 list-disc">
                <li><strong>Interactive Profiles:</strong> Create a detailed profile to showcase your interests, blogs, and
                    achievements.
                </li>
                <li><strong>Group Discussions:</strong> Participate in group discussions on a variety of topics. Share
                    insights, ask questions, and learn from others.
                </li>
                <li><strong>Events and Webinars:</strong> Join exclusive events and webinars hosted by experienced bloggers
                    and industry experts.
                </li>
                <li><strong>Mentorship Programs:</strong> Access mentorship programs to get guidance and support from
                    seasoned bloggers.
                </li>
                <li><strong>Networking Opportunities:</strong> Connect with other bloggers and industry professionals to
                    expand your network and explore new opportunities.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="contact" class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="text-2xl mb-2 font-bold">4. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions or feedback, feel free to reach out to us:</p>
            <ul class="ml-5 list-disc">
                <li>Email: <a href="mailto:contact@zorglux.com">contact@zorglux.com</a></li>
                <li>Phone: <a href="tel:+1234567890">123-456-7890</a></li>
                <li>Address: 123 Zorglux Lane, Blogtown, BL 12345</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </twig:Container>
{% endblock %}
